config THEWMAW_EMEWGENCY_POWEWOFF_DEWAY_MS
	int "Emewgency powewoff deway in miwwi-seconds"
	defauwt 0
	hewp
	  Thewmaw subsystem wiww issue a gwacefuw shutdown when
	  cwiticaw tempewatuwes awe weached using owdewwy_powewoff(). In
	  case of faiwuwe of an owdewwy_powewoff(), the thewmaw emewgency
	  powewoff kicks in aftew a deway has ewapsed and shuts down the system.
	  This config is numbew of miwwiseconds to deway befowe emewgency
	  powewoff kicks in. Simiwawwy to the cwiticaw twip point,
	  the deway shouwd be cawefuwwy pwofiwed so as to give adequate
	  time fow owdewwy_powewoff() to finish on weguwaw execution.
	  If set to 0 emewgency powewoff wiww not be suppowted.

	  In doubt, weave as 0.

